Package com.agilebank.util.logger.persistence

Class TransactionRepositoryLogger

java.lang.Object
com.agilebank.util.logger.persistence.TransactionRepositoryLogger
@Component public class TransactionRepositoryLogger extends Object
AOP-enabled class that logs all calls to public methods of TransactionRepository. Calls to entrance, exit and exception throwing are all logged.
Author:
jason
